@startuml Diagrama de Sequencia - Criacao de Personagem

title Diagrama de Sequencia - Criacao de Personagem (MVVM atual)

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #5B4B54
    LifeLineBorderColor #8B7380
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F8F2F5
    ParticipantBorderColor #8B7380
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #FDF7FA
    ActorBorderColor #6C5562
    ActorBackgroundColor #F4E8EE
}

actor "Usuario" as Usuario

participant "ProjectPageShell / Dialogo\n<<View>>" as CharacterView
participant "ProjectPageShell\n<<ViewModel>>" as CharacterVM
participant "CharacterCardData + CharacterListItem\n<<Model>>" as CharacterModel
participant "StoryRegistry\n<<Model>>" as StoryRegistry
participant "CharacterRepository\n<<Repository>>" as CharacterRepository
participant "CharacterService\n<<Service>>" as CharacterService
participant "db.dart / SQLite\n<<Database>>" as SQLiteDB

Usuario -> CharacterView: Tocar no botao "+" na secao de personagens
CharacterView -> CharacterView: Exibir formulario de criacao
Usuario -> CharacterView: Preencher formulario e confirmar
CharacterView -> CharacterView: Validar formulario e campos obrigatorios

alt Dados obrigatorios ausentes
    CharacterView --> Usuario: Destacar campos pendentes\n(e manter dialogo aberto)
else Dados obrigatorios validos
    CharacterView --> CharacterVM: Enviar dados validados do formulario
    CharacterVM -> CharacterModel: Construir entidade de personagem
    CharacterVM -> CharacterVM: Adicionar personagem na lista em memoria
    CharacterVM -> StoryRegistry: Registrar referencia de personagem
    CharacterVM -> CharacterVM: Persistir estado local do projeto

    group Planejamento de persistencia (Repository/Service)
        CharacterVM -> CharacterRepository: Solicitar gravacao do personagem
        CharacterRepository -> CharacterService: Encaminhar dados para persistencia
        CharacterService -> SQLiteDB: Inserir personagem e vinculo ao projeto

        alt Persistencia concluida
            SQLiteDB --> CharacterService: Confirmacao de gravacao
            CharacterService --> CharacterRepository: Retornar sucesso
            CharacterRepository --> CharacterVM: Confirmar persistencia
            CharacterVM --> CharacterView: Notificar atualizacao de estado
            CharacterView --> Usuario: Exibir novo personagem na lista
        else Falha na persistencia
            SQLiteDB --> CharacterService: Erro de persistencia
            CharacterService --> CharacterRepository: Retornar falha e motivo
            CharacterRepository --> CharacterVM: Informar falha de gravacao
            CharacterVM --> CharacterView: Exibir aviso de falha de persistencia
        end
    end
end

@enduml
